<section id="next-steps" class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Next Steps by Role</h2>

  {% if extend and extend.personas %}
  {% for persona in extend.personas %}
  <div class="ndx-persona-card govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">{{ persona.title }}</h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">{{ persona.description }}</p>

    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--spaced">
      {% for step in persona.nextSteps %}
      <li>
        <strong>{{ step.title }}</strong>
        <p class="govuk-body-s">
          {{ step.description }}
          {% if step.url %}
          <br><a href="{{ step.url }}" {% if step.external %}target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"{% endif %} class="govuk-link">
            {{ step.title }}{% if step.external %}<span class="govuk-visually-hidden"> (opens in new tab)</span>{% endif %}
          </a>
          {% endif %}
        </p>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
  {% endif %}
</section>

<section id="swindon" class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
  <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">The Swindon Story</h2>

  <p class="govuk-body">
    Simply Readable was pioneered by <strong>Swindon Borough Council</strong>, led by
    Chief Digital Officer <strong>Philip Murkin</strong> and Head of Emerging Technology
    <strong>Sarah Pena</strong>. What makes this tool special isn't just the technology -
    it's the people behind it.
  </p>

  <div class="govuk-inset-text">
    <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
      The Easy Read feature was co-created with <strong>Experts by Experience of a Learning
      Disability</strong> - a focus group of people with learning disabilities who tested,
      iterated, and validated the output to ensure it genuinely meets their needs. This
      user-centred approach achieved <strong>98% community satisfaction</strong>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Key statistics</h3>

  <div class="govuk-grid-row">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Document Translation</h4>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>Cost: £160 per document reduced to £0.07 (99.96% reduction)</li>
        <li>Time: 19 days reduced to 14 minutes</li>
        <li>Annual savings (Paediatric Therapy): £64,000 reduced to £27</li>
        <li>ROI: 6,300,000%</li>
        <li>75 languages supported</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Simply Readable (Easy Read)</h4>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>Cost: £120 per page reduced to approximately 1p per page</li>
        <li>ROI (Adult Social Care): 749,900%</li>
        <li>98% community satisfaction</li>
        <li>Co-created with Experts by Experience</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Adopted by councils across the UK and internationally</h3>

  <p class="govuk-body">
    Edinburgh, Newport, Southampton, West Berkshire, and councils in France have adopted
    the Document Translation tool. Simply Readable is gaining adoption as councils recognise
    the need for affordable Easy Read production.
  </p>
</section>

